title: The Mob Rules
description:
The Mob Rules is a full length skate video based in Ventura County and Los Angeles, California.
Featuring full parts Corey Walker, James Martin, Jake Langford, Eric Beltran, and Jared Martinez.
There is also a significant friends section including footage from Chad Anderson, Matt Lane, Chris 'Crusty' Weissmann and many more.
